join-based YES voting system
Wave behavior
Seeds or Primes can be attached
joining = approval (YES vote)
accumulation defines consensus strength



6. MINTING SYSTEM (STRICT RULE SET)

Core constraints
❌ NO allowance system
❌ NO burn
❌ NO selfdestruct
❌ NO liquidity / DeFi logic
❌ NO ETH stored in contract
✔ NO self-mint allowed
Permissionless mint rule
Minting is:
permissionless but requires gas cost
Meaning:
any address can mint to any other address
every mint requires Ethereum gas fee
no approval system exists
Atomic mint definition
Atomic mint means:
In one mint transaction, you can mint only the smallest unit allowed by the system (1 atomic unit of SOS)
So:
1 transaction = 1 unit mint only
no batch minting
no fractional minting
strictly minimal emission per action
Mint behavior
mint is always address → address
self-mint is not allowed
mint is a relational event inside the graph



